Class PhysicalObject

java.lang.Object
  lolwut.PhysicalObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Enemy, Item, Penguin, Platform, Portal
public abstract class PhysicalObject
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract class that represents all physical objects that can be displayed in Lolwut.

Author:
Daniel Wong
